When we setup our mail server to integrate with JIRA we gave it a default email address to use to send messages.  The problem with this is that when a message fails to get sent, the message delivery failure gets sent to the generic email address and the user doesnt know it fails.  Is there a way to set it up so that when an email is sent it uses the email address of the person logged in?

